It's 2017 and The Fingers of The Hand are up to no good! It's gonna take the combined strength of all of our Marvel Netflix heroes (minus Frank Castle) to stop them! Join us as we look back at the first meeting of The Defenders (Luke Cage, Daredevil, Jessica Jones, and....sigh...Iron Fist) as they join forces to tackle their hardest obstacle yet! In this episode, we talk about how the series fell short, what it got right, and what changes could have made this the Avengers level property it was meant to be in this in-depth review of The Defenders! Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [ComicBookClique.com](../episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media. Send us feedback at ComicBookClique@Gmail.com! You Are Worthy! Please [SUPPORT US ON PATREON](http://Patreon.com/CBCClubhouse)!

